quran[23{c,v,t}:
26,184,"aur uss zaat ka khauf karo jis ne tumhe aur guzashta naslon ko peda kya hai """
26,185,"unhon ne kaha"" to mehez aik sehr zadahaadmi hai"
26,186,"aur to kuch nahi magar aik ensaan hum hi jaissa, aur hum to tujhe bilkul jhoota samajte hain"
26,187,"agar to sacha hai to hum par aasman ka koi tukda gira day """
26,188,"Shoiab ne kaha"" mera rab jaanta hai jo kuch tum kar rahay ho """
26,189,"unhon ne usay jhutla diya, aakhir kaar chhatri walay din ka azaab un par aa gaya, aur woh barray hi khofnaak din ka azaab tha"
26,190,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar log maan-ne walay nahi"
26,191,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
26,192,yeh rab alameen ki nazil kardah cheez hai
26,193,usay le kar tairay dil par amanat daar rooh utri hai
26,194,taakay to unn logon mein shaamil ho jo ( khuda ki taraf se Khalq khuda ko ) mutnabba karne walay hain
26,195,saaf saaf arabi zabaan mein
26,196,aur aglay logon ki kitabon mein bhi yeh mojood hai
26,197,kya inn ( ehley mecca ) ke liye yeh koi nishani nahi hai ke isay ulama bani Israel jantay hain ?
26,198,( lekin inn ki hatt dharmi ka haal yeh hai ke ) agar ahem usay kisi ajmi par bhi nazil kar dete
26,199,aur yeh ( Fasih arabi kalaam ) woh un ko parh kar sunataa tab bhi yeh maan kar nah dete
26,200,isi terhan hum ne is ( zikar ) ko mujrimon ke dilon mein guzaraa hai
26,201,woh is par imaan nahi laatay jab taq azaab alim nah dekh len
26,202,phir jab woh be khaberi mein un par aa parta hai
26,203,"uss waqt woh kehte hain"" ke “kiya ab hamein kuch mohlat mil sakti hai? """
26,204,to kya yeh log hamaray azaab ke liye jaldi macha rahay hain ?
26,205,"tum ne kuch ghhor kya, agar hum inhen barson taq aish karne ki mohlat bhi day den"
26,206,aur phir wohi cheez un par aa jaye jis se inhen daraya ja raha hai
